snippet.title: AMBER HEARD is  a MOM - Hollywood TV
snippet.description:
Click to Subscribe! - http://bit.ly/SubHTV 
Hollywood TV is your source for daily celebrity news and gossip!
Surprise Amber Heard is a mom! The Aquaman star announced the happy news on Instagram.  "I'm so excited to share this news with you. Four years ago, I decided I wanted to have a child. I wanted to do it on my own terms,” Heard captioned a photo of herself cradling the newborn. “My daughter was born on April 8, 2021," adding, "Her name is Oonagh Paige Heard. She's the beginning of the rest of my life."

According to TMZ Gwen Stefani and Blake Shelton filed for their marriage license Tuesday in Oklahoma. You have 10 days from the date you file for a marriage license to tie the knot in Oklahoma. Sources told the outlet that the couple are set to walk down the aisle on Saturday at an outdoor chapel on Blake’s Oklahoma ranch.   Reportedly only close friends and family will attend the ceremony. 

James Franco has agreed to pay more than $2 million to settle a class-action lawsuit filed by former students alleging that female students at his Studio 4 Film School were sexually exploited. The lawsuit alleged that Franco’s acting and filmmaking school was actually a setup to provide a stream of young, impressionable women for sexual and financial exploitation. The former students claimed that Franco and his partners encouraged actresses to disrobe for explicit sex scenes and those who did were given preferential treatment.
